Задание 2

Go to first line in file:
    g  <  ESC-<       *  Go to first line in file (or line N).

Go to last line in file:
    G  >  ESC->       *  Go to last line in file (or line N).

Forward one window:
    z                 *  Forward  one window (and set window to N).

Forward one line:
    e  ^E  j  ^N  CR  *  Forward  one line   (or N lines).

Backward one line:
    y  ^Y  k  ^K  ^P  *  Backward one line   (or N lines).

Search forward for matching line:
    /pattern          *  Search forward for (N-th) matching line.

Search backward for matching line:
    ?pattern          *  Search backward for (N-th) matching line.

Repeat previous search:
    n                 *  Repeat previous search (for N-th occurrence).

Repeat previous search in reverse direction:
      N                 *  Repeat previous search in reverse direction.


Задание 3

/dev/null - character special file (символьное устройство)
/dev/zero - character special file (символьное устройство)
/dev/sda - ??
/dev/tty - character special file (символьное устройство)
/root - каталог
/etc/passwd - обычный файл
/proc/mounts - символьная ссылка
/bin/ls - обычный файл
/bin/zcat - обычный файл